{"tid":1804212,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"搵緊一本廣東話小說 求幫手","createTime":"2019-12-30T23:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T10:59:38.000Z","uid":326404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a7522c7ca14acc73d77c4d0ccf726c251428481f","tid":1804212,"uid":326404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T23:38:10.000Z","msg":"最近睇廣東話小說睇上腦<br />\n記得好耐之前睇過一本 作者叫凍xx<br />\n本書分兩個故事<br />\n<br />\n第一個係話係巴士上訓著咗<br />\n醒返個陣見到有條女係上層落嚟<br />\n追問下先發現佢係女鬼 後腦穿咗<br />\n跟住係床到醒返 以為係發夢<br />\n結果有電話打過黎 係夢境個隻鬼<br />\n仲要現埋身 跟住變左愛情故事<br />\n<br />\n第二個係話答飛機去到一個島<br />\n個機長迫降 然後有人介紹佢哋嘅任務<br />\n然後死左 跟住佢地一路做一路死人<br />\n最終任務係同下一架迫降嘅飛機介紹<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲記得本書或者作者<br />\n突然想睇埋佢其他作品"},{"pid":"f3a41fac0276b8170d79f6307c7f14d9c29170c8","tid":1804212,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:45:23.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJtOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=675a720b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJtOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=3cac224a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">1/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要23000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petitio